quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,55,tum un ke maal aur aulaad se taajjub nah karna. khuda chahta hai ke un cheezon se duniya ki zindagi mein un ko azaab day aur ( jab ) un ki jaan niklay to ( is waqt bhi ) woh kafir hi hon
  9,56,aur khuda ki kasmain khatay hain ke woh tum hi mein se hain halaank ho tum mein se nahi hain. asal yeh hai ke yeh darpook log hain
  9,57,agar un ki koi bachao ki jagah ( jaisay qilah ) ya ghaar o mughaak ya ( zameen ke andar ) ghusnay ki jagah mil jaye to isi taraf rasiyaan turatay hu-ay bhaag jayen
  9,58,aur un mein se baaz usay bhi hain ke ( taqseem ) sadqat mein tum par tana zani karte hain. agar un ko is mein se ( khatir khuwa ) mil jaye to khush rahen aur agar ( is qader ) nah miley to jhat khafa ho jayen
  9,59,aur agar woh is par khush rehtay jo khuda aur is ke rasool ne un ko diya tha. aur kehte ke hamein khuda kaafi hai aur khuda apne fazl se aur is ke paighambar ( apni meharbani se ) hamein ( phir ) den ge. aur hamein to khuda hi ki khwahish hai ( to un ke haq mein behtar hota )
  9,60,sadqat ( yani zakaat wa kherat ) to mflson aur mohtajon aur karkunaan sadqat ka haq hai aur un logon ka jin ki taleef qaloob Manzoor hai aur ghulamoo ke azad karanay mein aur qarzdaron ( ke qarz ada karne mein ) aur khuda ki raah mein aur musafiron ( ki madad ) mein ( bhi yeh maal kharch karna chahiye yeh haqooq ) khuda ki taraf se muqarrar kar diye gay hain aur khuda jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  9,61,aur un mein baaz aisay hain jo paighambar ko aeza dete hain aur kehte hain ke yeh shakhs nira kaan hai. ( un se ) keh do ke ( woh ) kaan ( hai to ) tumhari bhalai ke liye. woh khuda ka aur mominon ( ki baat ) ka yaqeen rakhta hai aur jo log tum mein se imaan laaye hain un ke liye rehmat hai. aur jo log rasool khuda ko ranj pohanchate hain un ke liye azaab alim ( tayyar ) hai
